subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: No. 1 Roger Federer followed Kim Clijsters onto the Arthur Ashe Stadium court and won his first-round match, 6-1, 6-3, 7-5, over the 18-year-old American Devin Britton.
